<br>
I wonder what kind of results you could get from attacking a red con guildtrainer NPC or similar.<br>
<br>
<br>
Vindicator is a quicker spawn. It might be frequent enough for testing.<br>
<br>
<br>
You know, the &quot;how hard it hits over time&quot; model might serve us better.<br>
<br>
What you could do is every time you tank the vindicator you could turn on your log and email me the log + your AC and agility at the time you tanked it.<br>
<br>
It would be a 3 axis plot. AC vs. average hit received vs. agility.<br>
<br>
But this could be plotted as a data point.<br>
<br>
If we could collect enough of these logs, we could construct a good surface plot which would show the effects of AC and agilty against the vindicator.<br>
<br>
Of course to make it happen we'd need a lot of people emailing me logs of their fight vs. a single mob. <br>
